As of the census<ref name=census2010/> of 2010, there were 75 people living in the CDP. There were 28 housing units. The [[Race and ethnicity in the United States Census|racial makeup]] was 78.7% White, 4.0% American Indian and Alaska Native, 14.7% from some other race, and 2.7% from two or more races. Hispanic or Latino of any race were 17.3% of the population.

